<!-- 忆闪 YiShan - 新手引导页 --><view class="guide-root"><!-- 步骤指示器 --><view class="guide-steps"><view class="step-dot {{index <= currentStep ? 'active' : ''}}" wx:for="{{steps}}" wx:key="index"></view></view><!-- 步骤内容 --><view class="guide-content"><!-- 步骤0: 欢迎 --><block wx:if="{{currentStep === 0}}"><view class="g-hero"><text class="g-emoji">⚡</text><text class="g-title">欢迎使用 忆闪</text><text class="g-subtitle">基于 SM-2 算法的智能闪卡学习系统</text></view><view class="g-features"><view class="g-feature"><text class="gf-icon">🧠</text><view><text class="gf-title">自适应算法</text><text class="gf-desc">SM-2 间隔重复，自动调整复习节奏</text></view></view><view class="g-feature"><text class="gf-icon">📊</text><view><text class="gf-title">遗忘曲线预测</text><text class="gf-desc">贝叶斯模型估算最佳复习时机</text></view></view><view class="g-feature"><text class="gf-icon">🎯</text><view><text class="gf-title">词汇量测试</text><text class="gf-desc">认知抽样算法，精准评估词汇量</text></view></view></view></block><!-- 步骤1: 如何学习 --><block wx:if="{{currentStep === 1}}"><view class="g-hero"><text class="g-emoji">📖</text><text class="g-title">三阶段学习法</text><text class="g-subtitle">每个单词都经历完整的认知过程</text></view><view class="g-stages"><view class="gs-item"><view class="gs-num">1</view><view class="gs-body"><text class="gs-title">认识新词</text><text class="gs-desc">查看单词、音标、释义、例句、谐音记忆</text></view></view><view class="gs-item"><view class="gs-num">2</view><view class="gs-body"><text class="gs-title">拼写练习</text><text class="gs-desc">主动回忆拼写，加深记忆痕迹</text></view></view><view class="gs-item"><view class="gs-num">3</view><view class="gs-body"><text class="gs-title">闪卡复习</text><text class="gs-desc">左滑已掌握 · 右滑再复习 · 点击翻转对照</text></view></view></view></block><!-- 步骤2: SM-2 算法 --><block wx:if="{{currentStep === 2}}"><view class="g-hero"><text class="g-emoji">🔬</text><text class="g-title">SM-2 间隔重复</text><text class="g-subtitle">科学记忆，告别死记硬背</text></view><view class="g-algo"><view class="ga-row"><view class="ga-card"><text class="ga-num">1×</text><text class="ga-label">首次正确</text><text class="ga-desc">1天后复习</text></view><view class="ga-card"><text class="ga-num">6×</text><text class="ga-label">第二次正确</text><text class="ga-desc">6天后复习</text></view></view><view class="ga-row"><view class="ga-card"><text class="ga-num">∞</text><text class="ga-label">多次正确</text><text class="ga-desc">间隔递增至180天</text></view><view class="ga-card"><text class="ga-num">↩️</text><text class="ga-label">回答错误</text><text class="ga-desc">回到1天间隔</text></view></view></view><view class="g-note"><text class="gn-text">每次复习后根据回忆质量自动调整下次复习时间，<text>越熟练间隔越久，不熟练就密集复习</text></text></view></block><!-- 步骤3: 完成 --><block wx:if="{{currentStep === 3}}"><view class="g-hero"><text class="g-emoji">🚀</text><text class="g-title">准备好了吗？</text><text class="g-subtitle">添加你的第一个单词，开始闪卡学习之旅</text></view><view class="g-ready-tips"><text class="gt-label">💡 小贴士</text><text class="gt-item">• 每天学习 10-20 个新词最佳</text><text class="gt-item">• 诚实评价回忆质量，算法才准确</text><text class="gt-item">• 发音 + 谐音 + 例句 = 三重记忆</text><text class="gt-item">• 连续打卡建立稳定的记忆网络</text></view></block></view><!-- 底部按钮 --><view class="guide-footer"><view class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" wx:if="{{currentStep > 0}}" bindtap="onPrev">上一步</view><view class="flex-1"></view><view class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="onNext" wx:if="{{currentStep < 3}}">下一步</view><view class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="onFinish" wx:else>开始学习</view></view><!-- 跳过链接 --><view class="guide-skip" wx:if="{{currentStep < 3}}" bindtap="onFinish"><text>跳过引导</text></view></view>